WEBVTT

00:00:00.630 --> 00:00:03.420
NINETEEN NINETY-FIVE

00:00:03.420 --> 00:00:07.060
MRS. Radovski, ir hot gezogt az di litviner

00:00:07.060 --> 00:00:10.150
hobn geshosn akegn di yidn in eyn un fertsikstn yor.

00:00:09.330 --> 00:00:13.220
yo, in eyn un fertsikstn yor

00:00:13.220 --> 00:00:15.100
fleg ikh aroysgeyn

00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:17.920
koyfn produktn.

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:22.890
mayn foter hot nit gelozn, vayl me hot hekhapt oyf di gasn, di me- di mentshn.

00:00:22.890 --> 00:00:29.140
nor mir hobn gelebt nit vayt fun fayer, fun pozha- vi zogt, nu, fun di

00:00:29.140 --> 00:00:31.730
ikh

00:00:31.730 --> 00:00:36.120
nu, v-, ikh gedenk shoyn nit oyf yidish

00:00:36.120 --> 00:00:38.930
UNK di fayer

00:00:39.012 --> 00:00:40.300
fayer leshers?

00:00:39.720 --> 00:00:41.480
ye fayer lesher, ye dortn.

00:00:41.480 --> 00:00:43.710
hot men gekhapt di mener

00:00:43.710 --> 00:00:47.000
un zey hobn aray- arayngelozn di kishkes

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:50.140
in moyl, un me flegt aroyslozn di vaser.

00:00:50.140 --> 00:00:53.480
zey flegn vern glaykh geshvoln, gefal-.

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:57.690
un ven ikh fleg geyn, flegt mayn foter shrayen "gey nit," vayl me khapt.

00:00:57.690 --> 00:01:00.660
felg ikh zogn, "ikh bin gegan mit nokh a khaverte mayne"

00:01:00.660 --> 00:01:03.680
zi hot gelebt nit vayt. idit, ide

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:06.190
Pavlovski ir familye gevezn

00:01:06.190 --> 00:01:07.725
Ida Pavlovski?

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:08.680
Pavlovski, ye

00:01:08.625 --> 00:01:09.910
ver iz zi geven?

00:01:09.910 --> 00:01:10.993
mayne a khaverte

00:01:10.999 --> 00:01:11.348
yo?

00:01:11.210 --> 00:01:13.720
yo, zi iz gevezn a blonde.

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:15.680
zi hot oykhet nit oysgezen a

00:01:14.728 --> 00:01:15.462
Ide Pavlovski.

00:01:15.680 --> 00:01:19.150
zi hot nit oysgezen vi a yidishe, flegn mir beyde geyn.

00:01:19.150 --> 00:01:21.890
un mir hobn ges- flegn zen vi me khapt di

00:01:21.890 --> 00:01:23.730
di mentshn,

00:01:23.730 --> 00:01:26.160
un me flegt zey paynikn.

00:01:26.160 --> 00:01:29.750
un dem, iz gevezn a gimnazye, a HEBREW

00:01:29.750 --> 00:01:32.370
gimnazye, a real-gimnazye.

00:01:32.370 --> 00:01:33.460
a real-gimnazye.

00:01:33.275 --> 00:01:33.859
ral?

00:01:33.990 --> 00:01:35.230
ye, gimnazye.

00:01:35.230 --> 00:01:36.760
ral iz a nomen?

00:01:36.090 --> 00:01:37.970
ye, fun di gimnazye.

00:01:37.970 --> 00:01:38.450
ral?

00:01:38.450 --> 00:01:39.510
real-gimnazye.

00:01:39.510 --> 00:01:40.521
R.A.L.?

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:43.140
ye, real, real, ye.

00:01:43.140 --> 00:01:46.010
dortn hot men gelernt HEBREW.

00:01:46.010 --> 00:01:49.200
iz, flegt men khapn di mener

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:56.760
un UNK zey flegn darfn mit di, mitn tsung oyselkn di gantse dil, vashn

00:01:56.760 --> 00:01:59.590
un iz Margoles, ikh ge- veys nit

00:01:59.590 --> 00:02:03.380
vi azoy Margoles hot gehat rekht tsu geyn ibern shtot.

00:02:03.380 --> 00:02:09.662
oder er hot gearbet shoyn mit di, mit di litviner, ikh ken dos nit zogn. ikh ken dos nit zogn.

00:02:09.676 --> 00:02:13.676
di mentshn vos hobn getsvungen di yidn dos tsu ton zaynen geven di litviner?

00:02:13.400 --> 00:02:17.518
di litviner, nor er flegt kumen, er flegt zey betn, "Maks,

00:02:17.518 --> 00:02:20.270
loz nit dayn meydl geyn in, in shtot.

00:02:20.270 --> 00:02:26.930
vayl me khapt dos." er hot alts gevust, mer af- mayn foter hot nit gekent aroysgeyn, er hot gehat moyre aroystsugeyn.

00:02:26.930 --> 00:02:29.420
nu, un eyn mol bin ikh aroys,

00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:32.930
un kh'hob zikh geshtelt in rey, in LINE.

00:02:32.930 --> 00:02:35.750
ikh mit mayn khaverte, nokh a shtikl broyt,

00:02:35.750 --> 00:02:38.770
un zaynen gekumen tsu loyfn litviner

00:02:38.770 --> 00:02:41.130
un di yidn hobn genumen loyfn.

00:02:41.130 --> 00:02:43.480
ikh hob gezen az zey loyfn, bin ikh oykhet gelofn.

00:02:43.480 --> 00:02:45.930
hot men undz alemen ongekhapt

00:02:45.930 --> 00:02:50.230
undz arayngefirt in a kloyster,

00:02:50.230 --> 00:02:57.140
un ikh hob gezen vi me me brengt mener mit froyen, yunge, oysgedreyt di hent,

00:02:57.140 --> 00:03:01.030
un eyne a froy hot ge- do, dan iz gevezn

00:03:01.030 --> 00:03:03.120
a rey daytshn.

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.190
dos hot men geton di litviner.

00:03:05.190 --> 00:03:06.830
ven zey hobn undz arayngekhapt.

00:03:06.830 --> 00:03:10.200
un dernokh hobn mir ge- gehert vi es geyen di daytshn.

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:13.260
zaynen gekumen zibn daytshn,

00:03:13.260 --> 00:03:16.010
un eyner hot genumen reydn daytsh tsu ir,

00:03:16.010 --> 00:03:18.730
tsu ir, az mir zaynen nit shuldik, gornit.

00:03:18.730 --> 00:03:21.520
hot eyner a daytsh gezogt azoy:

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:23.290
"me hot opgeshosn a daytsh,

00:03:23.290 --> 00:03:26.240
iz far eyn daytsh darfn mir hobn hundert yidn.

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:28.500
optsushisn."

00:03:28.500 --> 00:03:31.980
hot zi vos nokhet geredt, hob ikh gehert vi er hot gezogt,

00:03:31.980 --> 00:03:34.050
"mir muzn aykh alemen

00:03:34.050 --> 00:03:35.670
sh- opshisn, vayl

00:03:35.670 --> 00:03:37.640
Yisroel ken nokh onfaln."

00:03:37.640 --> 00:03:41.110
un ikh hob nit farshtanen vos heyst Yisroel.

00:03:41.110 --> 00:03:43.440
dan hot men gezogt "Yisroel."

00:03:43.440 --> 00:03:49.490
ikh hob gevust fun Palestine shoyn. ober Yisroel hob ikh nit, un zey hobn dos gezogt az "mir muzn oysshisn."

00:03:49.490 --> 00:03:51.730
nu, un dernokh di litviner

00:03:51.730 --> 00:03:54.000
hobn undz gefirt,

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:57.260
un undz avekgefirt oyfn Zibetn Fort.

00:03:57.260 --> 00:04:00.380
iz dortn iz gevezn shoyn zeyer fil leygn dershosene,

00:04:00.380 --> 00:04:02.650
rusishe plenikes,

00:04:02.650 --> 00:04:04.230
un yidn.

00:04:04.230 --> 00:04:07.450
un ikh hob dortn getrofn mayn lererke,

00:04:07.450 --> 00:04:09.260
Yofe.

00:04:09.260 --> 00:04:11.720
un zi hot derzen mir, hot zi gezogt "mayn kind,

00:04:11.720 --> 00:04:13.680
vi bistu do arayngefaln?"

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:17.030
hob ikh ir gezogt az, me hot undz ongekhapt.

00:04:17.030 --> 00:04:20.720
zogt zi mir "me shist ale tog nemt men aroys a grupe

00:04:20.720 --> 00:04:23.840
un me shist opet, nor,

00:04:23.840 --> 00:04:26.590
itst dershist men di mener mit di ki- yinglekh."

00:04:26.590 --> 00:04:29.820
yunge kinder. vos hobn zey geton, di litviner?

00:04:29.820 --> 00:04:33.430
zey hobn ale gedarft lign oyfn boykh

00:04:33.430 --> 00:04:35.830
un ven zey flegn onheybn shisn

00:04:35.830 --> 00:04:38.300
ir veyst, di, di UNK flegt zey gebn a treysl

00:04:38.300 --> 00:04:41.280
flegn zey glaykh trefn shisn in di mentshn.

00:04:41.280 --> 00:04:43.860
ober keyn eyne yingl

00:04:43.860 --> 00:04:46.680
un keyn eyn man iz nit aroys fun Zibetn Fort.

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:48.540
alemen hot men dershosn.

00:04:48.540 --> 00:04:52.540
nu, mir zaynen geblibn etlekhe kinder shoyn, me hot undz opgezogt,

00:04:52.540 --> 00:04:55.300
un oyf morgn hot men undz gedarft vayter shisn.

00:04:55.300 --> 00:04:57.540
hot zi gezogt "veyst,

00:04:57.540 --> 00:05:00.020
az s'kumt der glavner

00:05:00.020 --> 00:05:02.370
UNK," un dos gedenk ikh.

00:05:02.506 --> 00:05:03.171
UNK

00:05:02.930 --> 00:05:05.220
ye. efsher geyt tsu

00:05:05.394 --> 00:05:07.056
vu vu, ver iz er geven?

00:05:07.080 --> 00:05:09.980
er iz gevezn a glavner fun, fun di partizaner.

00:05:09.980 --> 00:05:12.680
fun di grupe fun naynt- fun Zibetn Fort.

00:05:12.723 --> 00:05:14.465
fun lit- fun di litviner

00:05:14.450 --> 00:05:16.070
fun di litviner.

00:05:16.070 --> 00:05:20.360
iz zogt zi "du un iditshke, zet nit oys vi yidishe,

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:22.590
efsher geyt aveket, fregn,

00:05:22.590 --> 00:05:26.480
reydn, ober ir zolt nit zogn keyn zakh az ir zayt yidn."

00:05:26.480 --> 00:05:28.330
un mir zaynen beyde gegangen.

00:05:28.330 --> 00:05:32.330
un ven mir zaynen gegangen, iz er geshtanen, er iz mistome gevezn a yor

00:05:32.330 --> 00:05:34.270
eyn un tsvantsik.

00:05:34.270 --> 00:05:35.520
tsvantsik.

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:38.140
ikh hob im gehaltn far a eltere.

00:05:38.140 --> 00:05:40.840
un lebn im iz geshtanen a yunger sheygets,

00:05:40.840 --> 00:05:42.410
un ven mir zaynen gegangen tsu

00:05:42.549 --> 00:05:45.740
hot er aroyfgenumen fun aksl dem biks,

00:05:45.740 --> 00:05:50.910
un er iz, un er gegang undz shisn, hot der UNK hot gemakht ot azoy,

00:05:50.910 --> 00:05:52.410
iberlozn.

00:05:52.410 --> 00:05:54.310
un ikh bin tsu

00:05:54.310 --> 00:05:56.759
un ikh hob gezogt "ikh vil geyn ahinter im."

00:05:56.759 --> 00:05:59.220
ober dos hob ikh farshtanen, gefregt "vu lebstu?"

00:05:59.220 --> 00:06:01.530
hob ikh gezogt "oyf an ander gas."

00:06:01.530 --> 00:06:04.600
kh'hob gehat moyre, efsher veln zey kumen in shtub.

00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:07.220
"far vos, vi azoy bist arayngefaln do?"

00:06:07.220 --> 00:06:10.480
zog ikh "kh'bin gegangen koyfn broyt."

00:06:10.480 --> 00:06:15.450
kukt er un kukt er oyf mir, un oyf ir, zogt er,

00:06:15.450 --> 00:06:19.390
"nemt un geyt, geyt aveket, durkh danet, ober geyt."

00:06:19.390 --> 00:06:21.990
dos iz geven aza groyser fort. "geyt!

00:06:21.990 --> 00:06:24.990
un ven ir vet araynfaln karik

00:06:24.990 --> 00:06:26.940
iz dan veln mir dir opshisn."

00:06:26.940 --> 00:06:29.380
in dem moment iz tsugelofn a froy,

00:06:29.380 --> 00:06:32.410
a yunge, mit a meydele fun a yor akht,

00:06:32.410 --> 00:06:36.380
un zi hot gezen az ikh reyd, un er redt azoy heflekh tsu mir.

00:06:36.380 --> 00:06:37.980
hot zi gezogt oykhet,

00:06:37.980 --> 00:06:41.540
"ikh vil aroysgeyn. mayn man hot zikh gekhavert mit

00:06:41.540 --> 00:06:43.010
SMETONA."

00:06:43.010 --> 00:06:47.100
SMETONA iz gevezn der prezident far di rusn.

00:06:47.100 --> 00:06:49.400
makht er mir "SMETONA?!

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:51.820
er iz gevezn a halber yi- zhid!"

00:06:51.820 --> 00:06:55.730
halber yid. un oyfn ort hot men zey beyde opgeshosn.

00:06:55.730 --> 00:06:59.960
di mame mit di meydele.

00:06:59.960 --> 00:07:04.880
ikh hob zikh zeyer dershrokn, un me hot, mir hobn gedarft geyn. un mir hobn

00:07:03.619 --> 00:07:05.714
ve- ver iz geven SMETONA?

00:07:05.460 --> 00:07:07.450
SMETONA iz gevezn der prezident.

00:07:07.619 --> 00:07:08.234
fun?

00:07:08.180 --> 00:07:09.340
fun Kovne. fun Lite.

00:07:09.488 --> 00:07:10.857
oh, fun Lite. SMETONA.

00:07:10.710 --> 00:07:15.080
un er iz take gevezn zeyer mit di yidn, mit alts, ye ye.

00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:17.680
nu, un ven mir UNK zaynen beyde gegangen

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:20.820
mir hobn gevelt aroysgeyn fun dem fort, un me hot gef-

00:07:20.820 --> 00:07:23.820
zaynen mir gekrokhn oyf ale toyte.

00:07:23.820 --> 00:07:26.880
zeyer fil toyte, un mir veysn nit vi me geyt aroys yetst.

00:07:26.880 --> 00:07:28.250
s'iz zeyer groys.

00:07:28.250 --> 00:07:30.850
un mir geyen un mir geyen, un mir geyen un geyen.

00:07:30.850 --> 00:07:33.120
un mir zaynen shoyn arayn oyf karik in fort.

00:07:33.120 --> 00:07:35.380
mitamol her ikh me ruft mir.

00:07:35.380 --> 00:07:37.860
di lererke, zogt zi "gey du arayn."

00:07:37.860 --> 00:07:39.870
"gey in di zayt."

00:07:39.870 --> 00:07:42.600
un mir zaynen gekrokhn, un mir zaynen aroysgegangen.

00:07:42.600 --> 00:07:45.870
nor ikh hob nit, mir hobn, dos iz gevezn oyfn barg.

00:07:45.870 --> 00:07:47.910
oyf a, oyfn grinem barg.

00:07:47.910 --> 00:07:50.920
dortn hot gelebt mayne a tante oykhet oyfn grinem barg.

00:07:50.920 --> 00:07:56.300
nor zogn vi tsu geyn hob ikh nit gevust, vayl ikh bin keyn mol nit gegangen aleyn.

00:07:56.300 --> 00:08:01.830
