00:08:01.830 --> 00:08:03.160
Kino DAINA.

00:08:03.160 --> 00:08:05.230
hob ikh derze- oyfn b-

00:08:05.230 --> 00:08:08.930
zeyer a groyser bild, Hitlers bild iz geshtanen.

00:08:09.083 --> 00:08:09.928
DAINA?

00:08:09.780 --> 00:08:11.080
yo, Kino DAINA.

00:08:11.080 --> 00:08:11.775
DAINA.

00:08:11.560 --> 00:08:14.890
yo. ven mir zaynen gegangen, un mir, ikh UNK

00:08:14.890 --> 00:08:18.290
