00:08:20.720 --> 00:08:22.760
vayl ikh bin keyn mol nit gegangen aleyn.

00:08:22.760 --> 00:08:26.860
dos iz nit gut gevezn. ikh hob nit gevust di gasn.

00:08:26.860 --> 00:08:30.530
