00:08:30.530 --> 00:08:33.160
ikh bin gevezn dortn

00:08:33.160 --> 00:08:36.390
in lag- in, in fort

00:08:36.390 --> 00:08:38.100
a vokh tsayt.

00:08:38.100 --> 00:08:40.000
nit gegesn gornit.

00:08:40.000 --> 00:08:44.450
me hot undz geshosn me hot nor gehert, m'hot gepaynikt, un gold, un gelt

00:08:44.450 --> 00:08:48.240
ver s'iz gelofn in Rusland hot men tsuzamengenumen, gebrakht do, un

00:08:48.240 --> 00:08:52.500
s'iz gelegn a hob mit a guts dortn oyfn nayn- oyfn Zibetn Fort.

00:08:52.500 --> 00:08:54.980
ir halt in eyn zogn iz "fort"

00:08:54.980 --> 00:08:56.560
dos iz a fort.

00:08:56.560 --> 00:08:59.154
dos iz a fort, dos iz nokh far far

00:08:59.154 --> 00:09:01.930
SMETONAS tsaytn hot men gemakht di fortn.

00:09:01.930 --> 00:09:05.830
dos iz in der erd.

00:09:05.830 --> 00:09:08.922
in der erd dos. dos, di komunistn hot men gehaltn.

00:09:08.948 --> 00:09:10.968
un vos iz es? vos... vil ikh farshteyn dos.

00:09:10.116 --> 00:09:11.389
dos iz

00:09:11.690 --> 00:09:13.580
vi zol ikh zogn?

00:09:13.580 --> 00:09:15.250
me hot gevizn aykh dem bikh-, nor

00:09:15.250 --> 00:09:18.920
shpeter vel ikh aykh vayzn dem bikhele, vet ir farshteyn vos iz der fort.

00:09:18.920 --> 00:09:20.730
ober ot zogt mir mit verter

00:09:20.730 --> 00:09:24.726
es iz a grob, oysgegrobn fun erd?

00:09:22.850 --> 00:09:24.780
ye, mit tsement,

00:09:24.780 --> 00:09:27.520
ot azoy gemakht in der erd,

00:09:27.520 --> 00:09:29.110
palates,

00:09:29.110 --> 00:09:30.870
un betlekh.

00:09:30.964 --> 00:09:34.690
un dos iz akegn bombes fun der luft, oder?

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:36.120
neyn, far di arestantn.

00:09:36.120 --> 00:09:39.360
dos iz far di arestantn, far di komunistn, far azelkhe,

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:43.482
dos iz zeyer, dos iz di ergste erter, nit in a turme, in a

00:09:43.482 --> 00:09:45.000
PRISON, vos s'iz do a

00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:47.670
a, nu, a tsimer, dos iz

00:09:47.670 --> 00:09:49.910
kalt un...

00:09:49.910 --> 00:09:52.920
un fintster, ye. nu, ye, finster.

00:09:50.160 --> 00:09:51.582
un fintster.

00:09:53.107 --> 00:09:57.059
un vifl mentshn voltn dan gekent arayngeyn in a fort?

00:09:55.970 --> 00:09:57.730
oy, a sakh.

00:09:57.730 --> 00:10:00.360
toyznter toyznter.

00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:02.190
zeyer groys.

00:10:02.190 --> 00:10:03.810
az ir zogt in Zibertn Fort...

00:10:03.810 --> 00:10:05.510
ikh bin gevezn oyfn Zibetn Fort.

00:10:05.510 --> 00:10:07.370
az zey hobn gehat

00:10:07.370 --> 00:10:10.142
numern tsi nemen?

00:10:09.080 --> 00:10:11.970
keyn zakh nit, nu, nit keyn numer, nit

00:10:11.970 --> 00:10:15.232
keyn nemen, UNK zey flegn kumen aroysfirn, opshisn. aroys...

00:10:15.166 --> 00:10:17.916
ober az ir zogt in Zibetn Fort...

00:10:17.410 --> 00:10:19.430
der, ah dos iz gevezn ye a numer.

00:10:19.430 --> 00:10:20.790
Zibeter Fort.

00:10:20.790 --> 00:10:22.420
s'iz gevezn Tsveyter Fort.

